title: Katla v2.2.5 - User Generated Content Theme
description:
Katla is a user generated content theme for WordPress made by Bluthemes. It offers the ability for users to submit content to your website via a custom made form. All the submitted posts are inserted as pending posts so a moderator can review the submission and do any changes if necessary. This is very similar to websites like 9gag.com and boredpanda.com, now you can easily make your own!
